title: Kingdom Rush Origins-PLAZA
description:
The most addicting tower defense game returns in an  all-new prequel
  adventure - welcome to Kingdom Rush Origins!  Kingdom  Rush  Origins
  is the third installment of  the award-winning  Kingdom  Rush  saga,
  loved by millions  and earning  accolades from  gamers  and  critics
  around the globe. Take a trip back to the beginning,  before  Veznan
  ever thought to threaten the  kingdom with  the gem  of  power,  and
  experience  even  more   of  the     lightning-fast,   exceptionally
  captivating  gameplay  that  made  the franchise  a  cornerstone  of
  essential tower defense games.

  For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/816340/
